cast.name: 阿玛拉·维拉富尔特 Amara Villafuerte

introduction: In the format of a well made "TeleNova", Luisa is an ambitious and charming lady who navigates men of all walks of life, in her own version of Sex in the City, Latin style. Luisa manages to get into some difficult - and hilarious situations - and with her curious charm, somehow she seems to get out of them too. A very comedic, expressive, and endearing character this lead brings to the screen (Luisa). A cast of 'regulars' portray her wide range of 'customer's' and most all are great at complementing her and making for a very interesting and watchable show
